{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "tech_team", "channel": "system_uptime", "user": "daniel_kim", "message": "Good afternoon team, I wanted to share with you our system's uptime performance for 2026. I'm pleased to report that our average uptime percentage was 99.6%, an impressive figure that reflects our ongoing commitment to system reliability.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "tech_team", "channel": "system_uptime", "user": "john_doe", "message": "That's great news, Daniel. This uptime percentage is crucial for our service reliability. However, we should remember it's not directly relevant to our data protection or compliance risk evaluation.", "create_at": 1620500000100}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "management_team", "channel": "strategic_planning", "user": "daniel_kim", "message": "Hi team, just to keep you updated, we achieved an average system uptime percentage of 99.6% in 2026. This is a testament to our technical team's hard work and dedication to maintaining service reliability.", "create_at": 1620500000200}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "management_team", "channel": "strategic_planning", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "Thanks for the update, Daniel. That's an excellent uptime figure. It's crucial to differentiate, though, that while this is key for service reliability, it's not a metric for data protection or compliance risk evaluation.", "create_at": 1620500000300}}
